Combine Simply Potatoes(R) and water in 4-quart microwave safe casserole dish. Cover; microwave on HIGH 10 to 12 minutes until potatoes are tender. Place Simply Potatoes(R) in extra large bowl. Add corn, celery, carrot, red pepper, olives and tomatoes. Meanwhile combine all dressing ingredients in small bowl. Whisk to combine. Pour over Simply Potatoes(R) mixture. Stir gently. Refrigerate 1 hour to blend flavors.